{"tid":846179,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中央政策組前顧問劉細良夫婦出版社　遭《炎黃解毒》作者入稟追版稅","createTime":"2018-10-03T08:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T00:25:06.000Z","uid":39464,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8fa1755167a0ed558bf5e64c9e5a985d41db9ace","tid":846179,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181003/s00001/39590e26c704d6acddfcc4b3ad3208fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181003%2Fs00001%2F39590e26c704d6acddfcc4b3ad3208fd.jpg&h=16cb889b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政經分析作者潘東凱稱，早前與由中央政策組前顧問劉細良及其妻鄺穎萱創辦的上書局達成協議，由上書局負責印刷、出版及發行其著作《炎黃解毒》，但上書局涉違反協議，沒向他支付該書的專利權費，故他昨日入稟區域法院，向上書局追討有關款項及要求交代帳目，並要求法庭頒令禁制上書局繼續出版、發行或銷售該書。<br />\n<br />\n原訴潘東凱在入稟狀指，2016年6月與被告上書局（Up Publications Limited）達成協議，由被告負責印刷、出版、發行及銷售原訴的著作《炎黃解毒》，並獲獨家發行及銷售權5年；劉與鄺則代表被告同意，將該書每本零售價128元中的25%即32元支付給原訴，作為專利權費。<br />\n<br />\n原訴續指，自協議後該書已售出超過6000本，惟被告違反協議，沒向原訴支付有關款項，即使原訴曾發律師信追討但不果，故入稟追討有關損失。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181003/s00001/1538552764734\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181003%2Fs00001%2F1538552764734&d=y20W634u0Ambr8VjUlsI4R4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=0b56026b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181003%2Fs00001%2F1538552764734&h=9c52d91e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181003/s00001/1538552764734</a>"},{"pid":"3c70b42932dc2dfc092ec69a735bd9628e5d204f","tid":846179,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T13:08:34.000Z","msg":"咁折墮呀"},{"pid":"029bdf035518beaf8ca30ef51f3a0ea1c3cb399e","tid":846179,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T13:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/n